<paragraph blockId="4.[178,1086,905,986]" pageId="4" pageNumber="803">D e s c r i p t i o n: Macropterous, brown, shiny, pronotum very finely punctate and with numerous puncture-like impressions on disc (fig. 12), elytra impunctate, pubescence short, semierect on pronotum elsewhere recumbent.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="4.[178,661,1002,1024]" box="[178,661,1002,1024]" pageId="4" pageNumber="803">
L e n g t h: 
<quantity box="[311,422,1002,1024]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.45" metricValueMax="1.5" metricValueMin="1.4" pageId="4" pageNumber="803" unit="mm" value="1.45" valueMax="1.5" valueMin="1.4">1.4-1.5mm</quantity>
(forebody 
<quantity box="[535,650,1002,1024]" metricMagnitude="-4" metricUnit="m" metricValue="8.5" metricValueMax="9.0" metricValueMin="8.0" pageId="4" pageNumber="803" unit="mm" value="0.85" valueMax="0.9" valueMin="0.8">0.8-0.9mm</quantity>
